"{\"uid\": \"femalefirst.co.uk-celebrity-pharrell-williams-olympics-party-disrupted-peta-protest-1403550.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"26 July 2024    Pharrell Williams' star-studded Olympics party in Paris on Thursday night (25.07.24) was disrupted by animal rights protesters.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 143, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 66, \"end\": 71, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 9.889771005159e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Pharrell Williams' glitzy party in Paris was disrupted by PETA protesters    The musician-turned-fashion designer hosted a glittering event for Louis Vuitton at the brand's headquarters in the French capital on the eve of the launch of the 2024 Olympic Games in the city on Friday (26.07.24) but the The Prelude To The Olympics bash was stormed by two supporters of PETA (People for the Ethical Treatment of Animals) who waved signs urging him to stop using animal skins in his designs for the company.\", \"from\": 145, \"to\": 647, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 145, \"end\": 162, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pharrell_Williams\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Pharrell Williams\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pharrell_Williams\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pharrell_Williams\"}, {\"begin\": 180, \"end\": 185, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 9.889771005159e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 289, \"end\": 302, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louis_Vuitton\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.987349675446497e-24, \"text\": \"Louis Vuitton\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louis_Vuitton\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louis_Vuitton\"}, {\"begin\": 338, \"end\": 344, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.8411031913781191, \"rank\": 0.18785461310675788, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"PETA Vice President of Corporate Projects Yvonne Taylor said of the protest: \\\"While Pharrell lives it up at celeb-filled soir\\u00e9es, the vulnerable animals sentenced to die for his 'fashion' choices languish in pain and filth on factory farms and at slaughterhouses, where they will be hacked to bits or skinned alive.\", \"from\": 651, \"to\": 966, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 693, \"end\": 699, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yvonne_De_Carlo\", \"score\": 0.9948769107545585, \"rank\": 0.002693736641281134, \"text\": \"Yvonne\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yvonne_De_Carlo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yvonne_De_Carlo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"PETA is calling on Pharrell to stop being complicit in cruelty and help pull Louis Vuitton out of the dark ages by shunning the antiquated use of animal skins and fur.\\\"\", \"from\": 970, \"to\": 1139, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1048, \"end\": 1061, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louis_Vuitton\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.987349675446497e-24, \"text\": \"Louis Vuitton\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louis_Vuitton\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louis_Vuitton\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The protesters held up signs emblazoned with the words \\\"Pharrell: Stop Killing Animals for Fashion\\\" before they were bundled away by security guards.\", \"from\": 1143, \"to\": 1292, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The event - held at the  Louis Vuitton Foundation - was attended by stars including Charlize Theron, Zendaya, Snoop Dogg and Serena Williams.\", \"from\": 1293, \"to\": 1434, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1318, \"end\": 1342, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louis_Vuitton_Foundation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Louis Vuitton Foundation\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\", \"Q33506\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louis_Vuitton_Foundation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louis_Vuitton_Foundation\"}, {\"begin\": 1377, \"end\": 1392, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlize_Theron\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.63137900383662e-32, \"text\": \"Charlize Theron\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlize_Theron\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlize_Theron\"}, {\"begin\": 1394, \"end\": 1401, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zendaya\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.3655065172342376e-24, \"text\": \"Zendaya\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zendaya\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zendaya\"}, {\"begin\": 1403, \"end\": 1413, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snoop_Dogg\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Snoop Dogg\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snoop_Dogg\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snoop_Dogg\"}, {\"begin\": 1418, \"end\": 1433, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serena_Williams\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Serena Williams\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serena_Williams\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serena_Williams\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Pharrell has been Louis Vuitton's men's creative director since last year and he previously incurred the wrath of PETA by creating a $1 million made-to-order crocodile-skin bag.\", \"from\": 1436, \"to\": 1613, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1454, \"end\": 1467, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louis_Vuitton\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.987349675446497e-24, \"text\": \"Louis Vuitton\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louis_Vuitton\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louis_Vuitton\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"PETA's US Senior Vice President Lisa Lange invited the musician to tour a crocodile factory farm to see how the creatures are treated prior to slaughter.\", \"from\": 1615, \"to\": 1768, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1615, \"end\": 1619, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/People_for_the_Ethical_Treatment_of_Animals\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.177200457923453e-30, \"text\": \"PETA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/People_for_the_Ethical_Treatment_of_Animals\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/People_for_the_Ethical_Treatment_of_Animals\"}, {\"begin\": 1622, \"end\": 1624, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9980467852526866, \"rank\": 0.0019289693638553625, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 1647, \"end\": 1651, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lisa_Simpson\", \"score\": 0.9999999984893293, \"rank\": 1.4682258021830937e-09, \"text\": \"Lisa\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lisa_Simpson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lisa_Simpson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She said: \\\"We'd like to invite you on a less-than-luxurious tour of a filthy (for that's what they are) crocodile factory farm with us to see the living origins of your 'Millionaire' bag.\", \"from\": 1770, \"to\": 1957, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"You'd want to bring along nose plugs and high boots to wade through fetid, waste-filled water.\", \"from\": 1959, \"to\": 2054, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If we go to an indoor tank, also bring a flashlight, because you will not see daylight.\", \"from\": 2055, \"to\": 2142, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There are no blurred lines here.\", \"from\": 2143, \"to\": 2175, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Killing wildlife for a bag is not cool - it's cold.\\\"\", \"from\": 2176, \"to\": 2228, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Tagged inPharrell Williams  \\u00a9 2025 FemaleFirst Ltd. all rights reserved.\", \"from\": 2230, \"to\": 2302, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"duration : 0.33934sv4.2 -2025-12-02 19:00:43\", \"from\": 2304, \"to\": 2348, \"entities\": []}]}"